title: X Fighter v1.0.1 Mod (Unlimited Everything)
description:
X-Fighter is an amazing air shooting game!

Players will command their fighters to conduct a final decisive air battle. It feels like you are fighting in the real hail of bullets.

Various weapons, different BOSS, looking forward to your challenge!
Destroy the enemy, become the most powerful ace pilots!

How to play:

1. Use your fingers to navigate.
2. Sheered away the enemy fighters and shoot down the enemy planes.
3. Earn gold coins to upgrade your weapons and life value.

Features:

- 12+ challenging levels.
- 10+ weapons and equipments.
- Shocking and gorgeous effects of slay explosion! 
- Smooth game play with arcade games!!!

What's New: (Updated: October 12, 2013)

fix crash bug.
